#> ...
#>           Date ConcLow ConcHigh        Q
#> 606 2011-09-29     0.8      0.8 13.90357
#> 
#> Choptank River:Inorganic nitrogen (nitrate and nitrite)
#> Parameter units: mg/l as N 
#> Drainage area: 292.6687 km^2
print(Arkansas_eList)
#> Daily discharge:
#>            Date     Q

#>

#> Parameter units: mg/l as N

plot(Choptank_eList)
plot(Choptank_eList, cex.main=0.7)
